message.body: Mark needs the car by 11:40 tomorrow morning. Did you want to meet a little earlier than 10? Does your dog(s) go for short walks or long walks? Do you have to do something afterwards anyway? I hate sharing the car like this!!! It's a new thing for me and it looks like it's going to be like this for a while...
Ah. Actually i do need to go earlier if at all. I have to be at the office by 945. Can we meet earlier?
Sorry. I was at dinner with my parents. Call me at like 730 and let's meet!
